data.description: Why wait for New Construction-This ALMOST NEW HOME (Built in End of 2020) is located in the highly desired LONG LAKE RANCH RESERVE NEIGHBORHOOD and nestled in the heart of Lutz. This exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-1/2 bath home combines contemporary elegance with functional design and features an open-concept layout. Just a few of the details that make this fantastic home even better include: a gourmet kitchen with double ovens, granite countertops, stainless-steel appliances, wood cabinets, an abundance of storage and counter space, spacious pantry, upgraded bathrooms with double sinks, covered extended double lanai, and so much more. Head out to your private completely fenced backyard for fun cookouts, gardening and just general relaxation. Enjoy the convenience of an interior laundry room with custom cabinets, an upgraded smart home/security system, an EV charger connection and new solar panels, resulting in super low electricity bills, significantly reducing your carbon footprint and saving you money. The Highly desirable LONG LAKE RANCH neighborhood offers unrivaled amenities such as 40-acre private resident lake for fishing and walks, 2 community pools and playgrounds. Walking trails, sidewalks and great neighbors are just a few of the reasons so many residents love living here. Super convenient location with easy access to the Veterans Expressway and close to area shopping and great restaurants. Don't miss the chance to make it yours—schedule a viewing today.
